MyBrand - Elevate Your Web Presence
This project contains a simple, responsive landing page template designed to showcase a modern web design agency or brand. It features a clean layout, a vibrant color scheme, and subtle animations to create an engaging user experience.

What's Included
index.html: The main HTML file containing the structure of the landing page.

style.css: The CSS file for all styling, including responsive design and animations.

Features
Responsive Design: Adapts seamlessly to various screen sizes (desktop, tablet, mobile).

Modern Aesthetics: Utilizes a vibrant color palette, gradients, and a clean typography.

Interactive Elements: Hover effects on navigation links and buttons for a dynamic feel.

Hero Section Animation: A subtle background rotation and text animations on load.

Font Awesome Icons: Integrated for social media links.

How to Run
To view this project locally, simply follow these steps:

Save the files: Save index.html and style.css in the same folder on your computer.

Open index.html: Double-click the index.html file, or open it in your preferred web browser.

No special server setup is required as this is a static HTML/CSS website.

Technologies Used
HTML5

CSS3

Google Fonts (Montserrat, Open Sans)

Font Awesome

Screenshots (Not Applicable)
As this is a code-only submission, no screenshots are provided. You can preview the design directly by opening index.html in a web browser.

